ARC TASK 981571dc
spatial reasoning puzzle 981571dc
the sea perceives training pairs then applies the rule to the test input

observe spatial_eye.rana
observe arc2_spatial_eye.rana

@filter task_colors
  "black"  "blue"  "red"  "green"  "yellow"  "grey"  "magenta"  "orange"  "cyan"  "maroon"

PERCEPTION arc_task_981571dc
energy 0.50
phase 0.00
spin 0.50
coherence 0.90
coupling 0.50

COGNITION arc_training_count_4
energy 0.60
phase 0.00
spin 0.50
coherence 0.80

@perceive task_summary
DETECT task_id: 981571dc
DETECT training_pairs: 4
DETECT test_inputs: 1

COGNITION arc_pair_981571dc_0_cyan
energy 1.10
phase 0.000
spin 0.50
coherence 0.90
coupling 0.00

